nodes.bodyText:
This was removed, we now use a 'data' call to gather this vpn security group via the following code in the mgm_stateless module:
data "aws_security_group" "vpn" {
  filter {
    name        = "tag:Name"
    values      = ["bfd-mgmt-vpn-private"]
  }
}

